* c) Duale di P
* -------------
*
*       max z = 2*w1 - 3*w2 + 3*w3
*       s.t.  +w1 + 2*w2 + 4*w3 <= -2
*             +2*w1 - w2 - 5*w3 <= +1
*             -3*w1 + w2 + 3*w3 <= -4
*             w2, w3 <= 0, w1 >= 0
